    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine is strong and the transmission shifts smoothly, ensuring a dependable ride for its next owner. While the exterior shows some light surface scratches and the interior has minor wear consistent with regular use, the car remains aesthetically pleasing and mechanically sound. It is a solid, reliable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that is ready for the road.",
