    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to the most exacting standards. This vehicle resides in a state of preservation rarely encountered in the secondary market, boasting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original showroom luster. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering the discerning driver an uncompromising experience. This is a definitive opportunity for those who demand excellence without exception.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
